<taxonomicName id="92A0B2A8192AB361ADAF8117772920C2" authority="L." class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Lilium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="null" pageNumber="553" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bulbiferum">
Lilium 
<normalizedToken id="D87AD0E3FA8C1A0B602BD3DA0B406D3A" originalValue="bulbíferum" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">bulbiferum</normalizedToken>
<authorityName id="16137210601FA96F2DA5D15B7BAABDF6" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">L.</authorityName>
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="5E811AAD2E2E8208CAB24A91CBCEDAAE" pageId="null" pageNumber="553" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="971F679570D65B53F9354B1450F75998" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Bulbillentragende Lilie</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="3CA6A164FC2F4A6F65EE2BB027642D54" pageId="null" pageNumber="553" type="description">
<paragraph id="45370A469C41DF2028B0B805CD0780A3" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="B88ED90B4AF00A0EA904663741E08BBE" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Lilium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="null" pageNumber="553" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="croceum">
<emphasis id="D2BE8E9EAF6323115849BDEA6F01F748" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">
<authorityName id="E91E154E5FA192CC098FB215DE9D1151" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">L.</authorityName>
croceum
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="D45CE378FA53170AAEC8DF6700B290D7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">
In den Blattachseln der obern 
<normalizedToken id="55D82D8833F25587EA0857455134E4B1" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
Bulbillen vorhanden
</emphasis>
(1-3 je Blattachsel); 
<normalizedToken id="C9B40D625FD5751B30EADD9FB5CC12EC" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Blueten</normalizedToken>
orange. - 
<normalizedToken id="7A3C67A6D2D3C17E3762461D5285FDEA" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="149E415ABA84F20AF67DEB6FE6037CDE" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">
<emphasis id="120E2AF7A948883BEAE411B5771D1569" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Zytologische Angaben. 2n = 24:</emphasis>
Wenige alte, aber 
<normalizedToken id="63CA5FE62496DED91629634CBEF64C79" originalValue="übereinstimmende" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">uebereinstimmende</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="539F3BD7F855EEFCE5269D7A43EB74AF" originalValue="Zählungen" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Zaehlungen</normalizedToken>
; Zusammenstellung von 
<normalizedToken id="55DFB199EF2A845C5CF4F0C38AF498ED" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="7CFA8144D4FD96A8D7528EE01E4FA1CA" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Loeve</normalizedToken>
(1961).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5A0805F55634C1C726735EA1698F1D13" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">
<emphasis id="59159555635063432F8FD43A94721E99" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Standort.</emphasis>
Montan und subalpin (1100-1900 m). 
<normalizedToken id="12F695B73DF8B749EAB57ABC970489EB" originalValue="Heiße" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Heisse</normalizedToken>
, felsige 
<normalizedToken id="A1E9A19339956BEB3DA7D1BBBB00B4C9" originalValue="Hänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Haenge</normalizedToken>
. Rosen- und 
<taxonomicName id="C15B4983871885A756DCC0649F78BA5F" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Berberidaceae" genus="Berberis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="553" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6487483B18811C5104D7058D9D2807A0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Berberis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="7AD345F4C63C6BDC0571BA6F1B0AA14D" originalValue="gebüsch" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">gebuesch</normalizedToken>
, Waldwiesen, Steinhaufen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CC1A9B5F6584F0BB6FDE341EFBFE6483" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">
<emphasis id="3244DE126C43CBB92B684DF5CFB60AD3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">
Verbreitung. Wahrscheinlich mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="F8E262F1142E758EDC3D6D82DA230B49" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken id="D6AF4D2AAC16DE92CED35EA7561189E0" originalValue="östlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">oestlich</normalizedToken>
): 
<normalizedToken id="C82132A6EBA5735231A37D0390CB674B" originalValue="Westwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Westwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Westdeutschland, Westalpen; 
<normalizedToken id="0D7BD90DAB0522E55C557DCF9DD22B09" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Norddeutschland, 
<normalizedToken id="B1FF10CD55297044FA9993CE6B16F23A" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Korsika, 
<normalizedToken id="4D303DB0C8B6CC0DB04094F0EF36C5A0" originalValue="Süditalien" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Sueditalien</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="2258AEFE20BAF065335B3FC904B5B9BD" originalValue="nördliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">noerdliche</normalizedToken>
Balkanhalbinsel, 
<normalizedToken id="5DA383310BB7BCF2E868BD0C46300411" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis in die Tatra. Verbreitungskarte von Meusel (1964). - Im Gebiet: Engadin, 
<normalizedToken id="F18F75B4ECC21D11C3E2FF8BE8F0C0CB" originalValue="Münstertal" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">Muenstertal</normalizedToken>
, Vorarlberg (Stuben), Oberinntal, Vintschgau; im Schwarzwald und in den Vogesen verwildert.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="829A9F40FF91D6C593ABB390247A7C85" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">
<emphasis id="E244E3C31DE0BD16DA2E04772EF2B5D2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">
Bemerkungen. 
<taxonomicName id="D5E882EC917BA4B814319DE2376972C3" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Lilium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="null" pageNumber="553" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="croceum">
<authorityName id="490702BD93C2A65499B5F3FD1074B69A" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">L.</authorityName>
croceum
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
und 
<taxonomicName id="95F375D4B89EADBE49580C916EA41C5B" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Lilium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="null" pageNumber="553" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bulbiferum">
<emphasis id="4300F131880F11E0D513B8FCB7B81AF1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">
<authorityName id="6DB4DFBDF6ECF54FD65B6F2D60A68011" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">L.</authorityName>
bulbiferum
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sollten zytogenetisch untersucht und die 
<normalizedToken id="2086C3D3446C7BA5C6E5B64EC1D47F1A" originalValue="ursprüngliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">urspruengliche</normalizedToken>
Verbreitung festgestellt werden. Beide Arten sind alte Gartenpflanzen und wohl in vielen Gegenden 
<normalizedToken id="FB2FE18AFF8E74319AA869BE1A174990" originalValue="bloß" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">bloss</normalizedToken>
verwildert und nicht 
<normalizedToken id="E8AA3E899C8FF692FEDAEB70325986FF" originalValue="ursprünglich" pageId="null" pageNumber="553">urspruenglich</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
